{"tid":1137323,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求意見]我應該可以點做？A0毒撚真係搞唔掂","createTime":"2019-05-03T16:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T18:43:18.000Z","uid":242406,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"824903a4b1f3705a17b682e3a792cf183671ee96","tid":1137323,"uid":242406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"半年前 番工識左個同事 然後我地就好快fd左<br />\n之後都有單獨食野嘅 然後開始有曖味嘅<br />\n跟住我慢慢開始中意佢<br />\n但係有一日我同佢講 我想識隔離部門個新男同事<br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:係咪上次見過佢同你講野嗰個呀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:佢幾好吖 幾高大靚仔 你咪去識下佢約佢囉<br />\n<br />\n之後我地就開始無野講啦<br />\n而且佢有一兩個月冇乜同其他人講野<br />\n依家好d 淨係同熟嘅人講野 有男有女嘅 <br />\n但就對住我唔講野 企埋一齊就好尷尬<br />\n但每次得番我同佢嘅時候 佢又主動講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢係一個幾被動嘅人<br />\n跟住我真係識左新同事呢條友 情人節仲一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但認識落都係唔岩 但都有keep住做朋友<br />\n但A0毒撚已經一路以為我中意呢個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟佢有無中意過我?<br />\n<br />\n利申:藍絲,毒撚已知我中意佢"},{"pid":"2a42fee617037a089652bb8f20266d2308611e4f","tid":1137323,"uid":152040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"唔好9up"},{"pid":"2cc1dc66bf7de23065d86b06ddbf0fbcf60a92ba","tid":1137323,"uid":35090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"同我做愛"},{"pid":"9e416d88e66a2a0f213efd5297abc8cde95a7258","tid":1137323,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"你話想識嗰個男仔嘅用意係乜？"},{"pid":"fb6d502d3dc0cb59f4715300af5b6d9c13334c6